Class ShortListList

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
Collection, List, Serializable
public final class ShortListList
extends org.apache.commons.collections.primitives.adapters.AbstractShortListList
implements Serializable

Adapts an ShortList to the List interface.

This implementation delegates most methods to the provided ShortList implementation in the "obvious" way.

public static List wrap(ShortList list)
